            "heading": {
                "type": "heading",
                "content": "Introduction",
                "level": 1
            },
            "items": [
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": "<p>Lesson aims and goals:</p>\n<p>You can match at least 8 English words with the correct picture:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>You have learned at least 8 English words that have to do with school.</li>\n<li>You know how those English words are spelled.</li>\n<li>You can put those words in context.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>You can use two of the structures taught correctly:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>You know the differences in the structures.</li>\n<li>You know why and when you should use which structure.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>You can write a letter of application using the right vocabulary and structures previously taught.</p>\n"
                },
                {
                    "type": "image",
                    "src": "https://maken.wikiwijs.nl/userfiles/8/8d5bc4dcb0bda321faeee34aee138be3a07d678a.jpg",
