        {
            "reference": {
                "value": "2745758"
            },
            "heading": {
                "type": "heading",
                "content": "Assignment 1 Vocabulary",
                "level": 1
            },
            "items": [
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": "<p>When you click on the link below you will go to a website with vocabulary exercises. Do all three exercises.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://learnenglishteens.britishcouncil.org/grammar-vocabulary/vocabulary-exercises/school\">http://learnenglishteens.britishcouncil.org/grammar-vocabulary/vocabulary-exercises/school</a></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span style=\"color:#008000;\">Group 1:</span> You can discuss your answers with your neighbour. Look at each others answers and compare them. What is the same, what is different?</p>\n<p><span style=\"color:#FF8C00;\">Group 2:</span> After 10 minutes we will discuss your answers.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n"
                },
                {
                    "type": "paragraph",
                    "content": "<p><strong>Finished?</strong></p>\n<p>Answer the question in the box below.</p>\n<p>Explain what your favourite subject is and what you like about it.</p>\n"
