                    "items": [
                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "content": "<h3><span class=\"underline\"><strong>Stones - Greeting &amp; ending a letter</strong></span></h3>\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/0kmNI_z2gDkcmFW3eAlsgBef3ZdS3RCPNKItfLfwdnptLQWaRqllEc8-VmVjOL6K1bZws4EPqOGSuE5GD0wK80BMThB63kRY9e-xQq4jHN2smYXW7zVTyR26Snkod791c6X8TcSf\" class=\"height-323-pixels width-580-pixels\"/></p>\n"
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "content": "<h3><span class=\"underline\"><strong>Guide for writing a letter</strong></span></h3>\n"
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "content": "<p><img alt=\"Write-Letter-Friend-Sample.png\" src=\"https://lh6.googleusercontent.com/awNUynS7jKUwZecZLPKawWmpzG7VyK7M5rfLztQi07YqbvkyrSUhqCFO3CltCUG0d-ouzegIyW81Xl3hrmMr6aaL_h65SqyR222xZGIKcy7yp4xfQfm0R-hYdkrXG3g9NZyFzNev\" class=\"height-779-pixels width-602-pixels\"/></p>\n"
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "content": "<h3><span class=\"underline\"><strong>Example of a formal letter</strong></span></h3>\n"
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "paragraph",
                            "content": "<p><img alt=\"Teaching-Assistant-cover-letter.gif\" src=\"https://lh5.googleusercontent.com/vcr8ddbeKcZNMD42FOcl7dwst1DeAfmJUeBdyfZEZfVBLp9SImPXZIjl4wwYJvXhCz1KFx7DKchoNJVfx8nhySV1c98mcHBG_ka73xPcSzF44nMf0lrhJlzsu5YOm8NOmS88wv07\" class=\"height-618-pixels width-550-pixels\"/></p>\n"
